{"tid":1107771,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"放下自然會自在","createTime":"2019-04-15T13:11:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T05:42:44.000Z","uid":41505,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f697d37de19c67ffb15b39894bd7765c89b97262","tid":1107771,"uid":41505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:11:13.000Z","msg":"明白分手後唔應該放棄自己，我選擇左改變自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令自己生活變得充實，做運動/搵朋友/睇書。<br />\n依家變得好中意睇書，仍然隔幾日就會食完lunch去附近書店睇書。<br />\n買自己想新嘗試既衫/裙，同事仲會讚我失戀之後著得仲靚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好中意呢個更好既自己，曾經有希望過佢會返黎，但依家會識得同自己講 由佢囉，自己一個人都可以，佢會搵返我先再算啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知道由依家起我會愛自己更多，即使以後我會再次愛上一個人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望失戀既各位，唔好再死纏你既前度，將所有心機放返係自己身上。死纏落去只會令佢覺得你越黎越討厭，只會令你地更唔會一齊返。如果真係有緣份，最後都會一齊。加油阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢一刻既我未係完全放下，但已經覺得今次做得好好，繼續努力。"},{"pid":"50f237d3a860e9372feb3ffe5b5160094939eb06","tid":1107771,"uid":215213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"加油啊，你做得好好"},{"pid":"398a4cb67023d821b6b58d0a3bdfd75a8f597ee6","tid":1107771,"uid":155360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb90f30cec2ff19dad6a042f80d6c9359ba5158a","tid":1107771,"uid":225267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"睇書真係會有種魔力"},{"pid":"2eea04fcad8b219a2c9004b392cd40710d8f1aaa","tid":1107771,"uid":41505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50f237d3a860e9372feb3ffe5b5160094939eb06","tid":1107771,"uid":215213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"加油啊，你做得好好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都覺！"},{"pid":"ff79e68d3245494c744c51c119d607d3a84f2574","tid":1107771,"uid":41505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398a4cb67023d821b6b58d0a3bdfd75a8f597ee6","tid":1107771,"uid":155360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:14:44.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:18:11.000Z","msg":"好似你既名就可以，去完成你既夢想！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04804614937c1fd455085daac209f5298de7ec84","tid":1107771,"uid":41505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb90f30cec2ff19dad6a042f80d6c9359ba5158a","tid":1107771,"uid":225267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:16:34.000Z","msg":"睇書真係會有種魔力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:19:34.000Z","msg":"即使我睇既仍然會有啲係港女心靈雞湯，但內容係咩唔緊要，文字本身就已經可以分散注意力。"},{"pid":"a21773440021ea88988e9b19aacb354c4a760921","tid":1107771,"uid":41505,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tLDk2DueeMI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtLDk2DueeMI&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUalSbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=dd8c3ff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tLDk2DueeMI</a><br />\n<br />\n一首我好中意既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732d5808d220185f658c8bc42be515c7e9913414","tid":1107771,"uid":137871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:44:12.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓主，要活得更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c006b940327036beff7d0396e8894d8f4d3454","tid":1107771,"uid":155360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff79e68d3245494c744c51c119d607d3a84f2574","tid":1107771,"uid":41505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"398a4cb67023d821b6b58d0a3bdfd75a8f597ee6","tid":1107771,"uid":155360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep